snippet.textDisplay: Heeyyyy Thanks for watching! OH, and I thought I made this obvious by hanging them on the wall, but these palettes are meant to be decoration, I'm not going to use them anymore 😂  I keep getting questions about how they will "hold up" when they get used. They are officially retired now 😂 Also to address some of the other comments: no, it's not "wasteful" to use a paint palette as decoration instead of using them as intended. It's no more wasteful than painting on canvas and using it as decoration. 🤷‍♀️
